{"tid":1427186,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"建議］有關最新公告一事","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:10:20.000Z","uid":76216,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2389e87a432ea5cf1ed3abaa06fbed1f6dae7f40","tid":1427186,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"回應會員對本討論區評分系統及對管理團隊的各種查詢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1424552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1424552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nadmin提到，p牌正洗負評比例唔高，主要係舊會員投票，所以唔存在p牌帶風向投票。<br />\n<br />\n其實咁嘅推論係錯的，因為你提出嘅data只係<br />\n（結果）而唔係一個有時序嘅統計，因為有可能就係因為一開po，幾百p牌入去洗評價，其後舊會員見到就會羊群心理跟住岩岩所見嘅正負評比例去投票。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">只用（結果）去推論的話，其實仲可以話3毛用幾百人就帶動幾千舊會員風向。</span><br />\n<br />\n要真係排除唔係有p牌帶風向，可以用時序統計黎睇，例如  開po後30分鐘做統計，幾多人投正負評，1個鐘頭之後又係幾多，咁先睇到個發展曲線，咁個統計先有意義，<span style=\"color: red;\">只用結果黎推論判斷係十分</span>錯誤！！"},{"pid":"4803afe7408a103fdaeb3f6c0a1cd2ac733d5e09","tid":1427186,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a439791da2cd5a1edd9654d7d10d4a2702a70d","tid":1427186,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"淋病巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104afefa4f4f192aae906c24bbd62389f3a6cec6","tid":1427186,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a439791da2cd5a1edd9654d7d10d4a2702a70d","tid":1427186,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"淋病巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"身為一個知識份子 <br />\n要講得出邊到出問題<br />\n同點樣解決<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a